## ğŸ“‚ Project Workflow

1. Text input (raw paragraph)
2. Sentence & word tokenization
3. Text cleaning using regex
4. Lowercasing
5. Stop word removal
6. Stemming & Lemmatization
7. Feature extraction using:
   - Bag of Words
   - TF-IDF

